phrases: The Scale Festival starts tomorrow, huh?
It is our first festival in Akihabara, after all.
many guilds have been making special items for the event.
Licensed by the Round Table Princess Figures (Wood Carved)
Just hearing there is a festival makes a lot of people want to do something.
You have got quite a lot there.
They will not even fit in my magic bag.
The Crescent Moon Alliance will be selling winter clothes?
We are having a fashion show, as well.
It starts tomorrow, so we are doing the final touches today.
I heard Crescent Moon Burgers will be making their return.
So, what will you be doing during the festival?
I will be going around and enjoying all the different shops.
Come to think of it, I did not hear.
What will the girls be doing?
All-You-Can-Eat Cake Buffet Come as a couple, and get in free!!
I have only made it this far because of you.
All-You-Can-Eat Cake Buffet Come as a couple, and get in free!!
Shutting yourself up in here again?
Handling the Round Table's paperwork, investigating this world...
I ate two hours ago, and I took a fifteen-minute nap.
You did not need to bring it.
If you had just sent a message, I would have come to get it.
So you say, but would you really have come?
I have heard you have been locked in here for ages,
so I wanted to check on you, too.
How is the Scale Festival looking?
He is really taken charge of the event.
You should take a break for these next three days.
During the festival, it will be pretty noisy,
so I probably will not be able to concentrate...
This is a good chance for you to become closer to your guildmates.
Log Horizon is one of the Round Table guilds.
You will be out there, making the event fun, right?
Akatsuki and Minori are so cute, too.
An Akatsuki doll that Akatsuki gave me!
Truly, as long as I have my fantasies, I barely even need to eat!
They say that man does not live by bread alone.
But with bread and fantasies, you can get over almost anything!
You are just playing around, are not you?
During the festival, it will be hard to do much.
When reports come in, I will have to do some fancy footwork,
so I will end up waiting, anyway.
Since then, nothing has happened in Minami...
You want a red bean bun?
It feels like forever since I was outside.
In this world, red bean buns are expensive.
I want you to eat them.
It is been a long time since I have had one.
There is bean paste on your mouth.
What are you going to do during the festival?
Oh, I will probably have to help with things.
My lord, do you like c-c-ca...
All-You-Can-Eat Cake Buffet Come as a couple, and get in free!!
So, about the Scale Festival tomorrow...
Would you go to this with me?
You enjoy sweets, do not you?
From the way he eats his red bean buns, that would seem to be true.
I certainly do not dislike them...
If we go as a couple, it is free!
There is a pre-festival dance tonight.
I will be going out with Shiroe tomorrow,
but I am not sure what to wear.
I do not think I have seen him outside for a week.
Well, if you win this contest,
you get two tickets to the Twilight Banquet with Princess Lenessia on the second day.
Participants compete to see who can eat the most slices!
The top two teams advance to the final battle!
They say they do not know what he is thinking...
But he is actually really nice.
I am sad that they do not understand him.
I want them all to know more about him.
Why does Minori have to put pressure on me?
Even if he does normally treat me like a kid, this does not seem fair...
Is it my lord's fault for treating me as a kid?
My lord did not judge me based on my appearance or level.
He accepted me for who I am...
My lord said he would attend the buffet with both Minori and me.
But it is supposed to be a couple, so we will probably be alone...
What do you suppose is going on?
It is getting lively around here.
What am I going to wear?
Oh, I will ask someone to help me.
Crafting Guild Council Office Knock First!!
That is going to be expensive.
The Council does not play favorites.
Your location is determined by lottery.
Hey, you are doing all that yourself?
I do not have a choice.
This place is like a business congress.
I asked everyone to submit them
so I could check for any dangerous items.
The People of the Land's merchants are also coming.
I am getting the sense that the festival is a lot bigger than it should be.
The next few days are going to be hell...
Sorry to ask this of you...
Oh, if that is the case, I understand.
I am sure this will be difficult for you...
I am glad all three of us could get in together.
I just got permission from Kanako, the organizer.
We will have to eat twelve to enter as a trio, but I think we can do it.
Let us win, and go to the finals!
To be honest, I do not think I could have eaten here twice.
That is a wonderful kimono, Akatsuki.
It is rare to see you in a kimono.
A guild called Kimono Komachi made it for me...
It is graceful, and really nice.
Yes, she took me to a bunch of stores.
Why do not you come with us sometime?
Isuzu knows a lot about clothes.
I have high hopes for this!
Yeah, I think I could eat four of those.
It is a little present from my guild!
It is not fair that you got to bring two!
Is he trying to show off?
I will get them both involved.
I need to avoid making a fuss.
Am I supposed to eat that?
Come on, it will fall off.
Well, yeah, it is good, but...
I would rather fight a dozen raid bosses at once!
We could not eat them all.
Will you go home and rest, my lord?
I was going to see the rest of the festival, but I think I will...
You two go on without me.
I need to make a stop before going back.
Dandelion barley tea is good for digestion, right?
I am sad I could not attend the Twilight Banquet,
but Shiroe worked hard for me.
I will have to thank him.
Three people eating twelve whole cakes?
It will probably be there tomorrow.
I wonder how many whole cakes he will end up eating...
But all the girls love Soujirou,
yet he still does well running his guild.
Naotsugu or Chief Nyanta seem more like guild masters than I do.
I do not really have the presence.
Maybe Henrietta's right, and this would be a good chance.
I should make time to spend with everyone.
The town is even more lively than usual.
It is a festival, after all.
When we first arrived in this world, I never would have imagined it.
Or did you not have fun?
Anyway, I am sorry we did not get to the finals.
That does not matter to me.
It was Minori who wanted to go.
But was that cake okay with you?
It felt like I was doing all the eating.
I was not there for the cake.
It is hard to hold a conversation with you, my lord!
I do not know what to say.
You just do not talk much.
I have all sorts of things to discuss.
Then give us something to talk about.
It is fun to do this.
Is this part of her lord-and-servant role playing?
How could I have said that?
You are just now figuring it out?
It was obvious to the rest of us.
He is nice, and he is caring.
I can see why you would admire him.
I do not think it is a problem.
I have not lost anything, and I have not done anything.
I have not done anything yet, have I?
She wanted to be like him...
But it did not take long for those feelings to turn to love.
Minori is in love with Shiroe.
Next time: Student of the Mage.
